reviewText: I ordered a book and instead I received a DVD. I only have a DVD player on my computer which is not anywhere near my sewing area. I wanted the book because I could pick up and read the parts any time.

Quilt in a day? Dare to dream. Although my  sewing isn't that speedy I'm happy to use Eleanors methods. Im a very visual learner and this is the first sewing instructions that didn't have me pulling out my hair and calling my mom for help every five minutes. I hope I'm still stripping when I'm Eleanors age:).
